      <p class="text-sm mb-8" style="color:#94a3b8">Last updated: January 11, 2023</p>

      <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 p-8 flex flex-col gap-6" style="background-color:#132d52; color:#94a3b8">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">General Disclaimer</h2>
          <p>NETSums provides general information only. The Company assumes no responsibility for errors or omissions in the contents of the Service.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>NETSums is not liable for any damages arising from the use of this Service. We reserve the right to modify or remove content at any time without notice.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">External Links</h2>
          <p>We do not guarantee the accuracy or completeness of any external websites linked from this Service.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Fair Use</h2>
          <p>Any copyrighted material used on this Service is used under fair use provisions. Users must seek permission for any other use.</p>
